{"tid":845236,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)絕世天劫 太陽浩劫 地心浩劫","createTime":"2018-10-02T13:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T19:34:57.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5c72271aed79597f7db8d69397a2b07b29d2a7c0","tid":845236,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:24:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=ID3nO0r94eMTix5iJD65QQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=a445c8dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=ID3nO0r94eMTix5iJD65QQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=327a8544\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=ID3nO0r94eMTix5iJD65QQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=5f419ed9\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fc/Armageddon-poster06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffc%2FArmageddon-poster06.jpg&h=891e86ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/68/Sunshine_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F68%2FSunshine_poster.jpg&h=a11d3b7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/f/f4/The_Core_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Ff%2Ff4%2FThe_Core_poster.jpg&h=5d51b01f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.地球即將被跟德州一樣大的隕石撞擊，為了毀滅隕石，美國國家航空暨太空總署決定派人在隕石上挖一個洞直到核心，放一顆炸彈在裡面引爆，從內部炸開隕石。布魯斯威力演的史哈利在中國擁有油田，是公認成功的石油大老闆。他並不信任他一個年輕屬下小傑，因此也不爽他女兒蕾跟他交往..<br />\n<br />\n2.故事講述在西元2045年時，太陽活動逐漸減緩並快將熄滅，地球逐漸冰封，人類和地球面臨滅亡的命運，科學家決定將質量相當於曼哈頓的恆星炸彈（stellar bomb）向太陽投射，並將之引爆，試圖太陽重新運作再生。<br />\n2057年，載有八名船員的「伊卡魯斯2號」（Icarus Ⅱ）太空船自地球出發，負責運送巨型炸彈，執行拯救人類的任務。在航行到水星附近時突然接收到奇怪信號，並找到七年前神秘失蹤的「伊卡魯斯1號」太空船。在航向太陽的旅途中出現了種種問題，船員們對於執行任務的責任感和死亡恐懼的衝突、供氧植物意外被燒毀、航行的設定修改出錯...等等，而其中發生的意外事故甚至導致有船員在中途不幸犧牲。在搜索「伊卡魯斯1號」的行動中，由於連結裝置意外崩毀，也造成了船員犧牲<br />\n<br />\n3.電影講述地球的核心因不明原因停止轉動，以致電磁場減弱。地球若失去地磁的保護，將遭到致命的高能宇宙微波輻射襲擊，造成災難。此時由六人組成團隊，駕駛一艘名為「維吉爾號」的潛地艇，鑽進熾熱地函，放置並引爆核彈，使地核再次轉動以重生地磁<br />\n<br />\n11 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=ID3nO0r94eMTix5iJD65QQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=419485d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=ID3nO0r94eMTix5iJD65QQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=f7adff6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69354cbc1bd458c45a55469d5b6eaa05